Step 1 : reboot the server


Step 2: on grub prompt press edit(e) for the kernel


Step 3: 
	locate line with /vmlinuz entry
	on this line replace rhgb quite  with init=/bin/bash

Step 4: 
	press CTRL+x
	to boot

Step 5: 
	when on # prompt 
	mount -o remount,rw /

Step 6: 
	passwd root
	change the password

Step 7: 
	touch /.autorelabel



   


 
